checkHash

public final void checkHash(com.google.gson.JsonElement json,
                            java.lang.String hash,
                            T element)
Checks that the passed hash is equal to a new computed one if the option SerializationOption#IGNORE_HASH_CODE is set.

If the computed hash is not equal to the given one a warning will be added in the list of warnings.

Parameters:
hash - Hash in string representation
element - Element for which a new code to be generated
